type SolutionData = {
annotations: Array<Annotation>
videoCodes: Array<VideoCodes>
cutList: Array<Cut>
customVideoCodedPool: Array<CustomVideoCode>
}
type Annotation = {
start: string
end: string
text: string
memo: string
color: string | null
}
type VideoCode = {
start: string
end: string
text: string
memo: string
color: string | null
idFromPrototype: string
}
type Cut = {
start: string
end: string
text: string
memo: string
color: string | null
url: string
offset: number
playbackRate: number
}
type CustomVideoCode = {
id: string
name: string
description: string
color: string
parentId: string | null
userCreated: boolean
videoCodes: Array<CustomVideoCode>
}
